						<td><span class="pn-normal"><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="index.php" title="Back to the home page.">Home</a><br /><br /><b>Submit</b><br /><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=Submit_News&amp;file=index" title="Submit an article.">New Article</a><br /><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="modules.php?op=modload&name=Downloads&file=index&req=AddDownload" title="Submit a download.">New Download</a><br /><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="modules.php?op=modload&name=Web_Links&file=index&req=AddLink" title="Submit a weblink.">New Weblink</a><br /><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="modules.php?op=modload&name=Web_Links&file=index&req=AddLink" title="Submit your guild's website.">New Guild Link</a><br /><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="index.php?module=My_eGallery&do=upload" title="Submit screenshots to the gallery.">New Screenshot</a><br /><br /><b>Community</b><br /><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="modules.php?op=modload&name=Web_Links&file=index&req=viewlink&cid=2" title="Visit guild links for Luclin.">Guild Links</a><br /><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="http://www.eqluclin.com/forum/" title="Go to the Luclin Message Board.">Message Board</a><br /><br /><b>Site Tools</b><br /><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="index.php?module=archives&amp;func=main" title="">Archives</a><br /><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=Downloads&amp;file=index" title="Check the list of downloads.">Downloads</a><br /><strong><big>&middot;</big></strong>&nbsp;<a class="pn-normal" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=Web_Links&amp;file=index" title="Check out links to other sites.">Web 